{"title": "There is a way - INTA Meditation", "author": null, "url": "https://veranstaltungen.freiburg.de/events/en/e-es-gibt-einen-weg-inta-meditation?widgetToken=2UvrbVzILvI.&source=standalone&", "hostname": "freiburg.de", "description": null, "sitename": "veranstaltungen.freiburg.de", "date": "2023-03-16", "id": null, "license": null, "body": null, "comments": "", "commentsbody": null, "raw_text": null, "text": "Courses & workshops\nThere is a way - INTA Meditation\nFriday, 24/03/2023\n/\n[Waldhof e.V. - Academy for Continuing Education](https://veranstaltungen.freiburg.de/events/en/el-waldhof-ev-academy-for-continuing-education-983?source=standalone&widgetToken=2UvrbVzILvI.&)\nThere is a path that no one goes if you don't go it.There is your path,a path that arises if you go it.Werner SprengerIn meditation I experience myself in the deep perception of my feelings, my thoughts and my body. I find connection to the sources of my strength and thus find the courage to live even unlived life and to go my own way alive - in love and respect for myself, for the people closest to me and for the world in which I live.INTA meditation is a path that has grown in thousands of years of tradition. In it I encounter myself and recognize myself in a protected space of trusting encounters with other people. In these mindful encounters, my self-confidence grows, and my capacity for sincere and lively relationships grows. I learn more and more to trust my feelings and my thoughts, and to live the experiences of my life in a new and conscious way, even in everyday life. I will also be able to face new challenges in a more healing way.\nCourse leader: Aeschlimann, Tanja. Speakers: Helga Sprenger has accompanied people for decades with Werner Sprenger, the founder of INTA meditation, she is the author of the book Wenn die Seele aufatmet.Monika Barth is a certified meditation teacher.More at www.INTA-Meditation.de", "language": null, "image": "https://seminar-eins5.de/data/WHF/bild.JP